Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: "The Parallelized Way of Regression Analysis"
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jeffrey Ugochukwu
Maintainer: <jnugochukwu@ucdavis.edu> 
Description: "This package applies parallel computing to conduct Regression 
    Analysis on continuous datasets. The core functions build faster linear
    regression models and conduct confidence intervals to measure where the true
    mean datapoint lies between an interval."
